{
  "stem": "10699.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was just getting married, and he had a family, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yet-- and he didn't want to die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And yet, and he died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I felt bad for him, that he had died so young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt bad because the children missed a wonderful father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and, then, of course, then everything changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was terribly unhappy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very, very depressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I must say, I had hardly any support.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No support.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because you didn't know people?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did know very few.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I live in the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The few people I knew were very good, once I made friends with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's amazing, in circumstances like that, how his old friends were not supportive at all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my English wasn't that good, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't say that after two and a half years it was that good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't used to dealing in-- in-- in anything concerning bills or anything, banking or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All that was strange still to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And although I had my family, you know, the cousins, but I was still on my own, terribly on my own.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I considered, one time, to go to France, but I wanted to bring them up religiously, because that's what my husband wanted for his daughters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had also some-- some rights, which I had to see to, which didn't permit me just to leave everything and go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that it took me, really, another 20 years till I got part of my rights.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a 20 year fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was financial things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Financial fight, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, I had already brought up my children, by that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a very, very hard time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was just financially very difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a lonely life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was also a life where I was scared to marry again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I now realize that there were many factors why I didn't marry again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I had the impression, at the time, whatever I touch, I lose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You get that feeling that you love something, or you love somebody, and it goes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You lose it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It leaves you with a trauma.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you mustn't forget that I still had terrible nightmares.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was still not that well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I have had two little one-- children, that needed me badly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they have difficulties, because they know what I went through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I find it just, still, to this day, difficult for them to read about it, or watch anything about it, because they know this their mother went through that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they can't cope with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why I do it, really, is for the next generation, and for the other, for later, that people shouldn't forget.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the last thing we must do is forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't do it for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We feel a guilt complex.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's a terrible thing that I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If we don't do it, we feel guilty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If we do it, we feel bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You feel ill.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And yet, we feel we have to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because, in the memory of the ones that didn't come back, we feel, all the time, that we have more than a duty.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's something-- we are here because we must tell the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think that it is something this is forever with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what people don't understand, is that when we watch something, we always see something else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The others' flesh is constantly with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And yet, you have to try and make a life for yourself.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
